--NAME--
NGSIv2 geo-queries for entities located with geo:point

--SHELL-INIT--
dbInit CB
brokerStart CB

--SHELL--

#
# 01.  Create point A (5, 5)
# 02.  Create point B (9, 5)
# 03.  Create point C (15, 5)
