# 16b. Query disjoint (same) box (-5, 11) (6, 0) -> B, C, D
# 17.  Query disjoint polygon (0, 0) (24, 0) (0, 20) -> D, E
# 18.  Query equals point (15, 15) -> D
# 19.  Query equals line (5, 5) (9, 5) -> none
# 20.  Query equals box (-5, 0) (6, 11) -> none
